+## 1. System Topology
+
+Primary agents and channels:
+
+- `Jarvis Root Admin` โ€” orchestrator and final synthesizer
+- `Gemini CLI Agent` โ€” research + external context
+- `Codex CLI Agent` โ€” structured analysis + execution blueprint
+- `Claude CLI Agent` โ€” risk/quality gate
+- `Facebook Extension` โ€” automation plugin
+- `LINE Bot` and `Telegram Bot` โ€” user-facing messaging channels
+- `Dashboard` โ€” web-based admin UI (React + Vite + TailwindCSS)
+- `Jarvis Terminal` โ€” xterm.js web terminal via WebSocket
+
+High-level message flow:
+
+1. User message enters LINE/Telegram/Dashboard/Terminal.
+2. Messaging bridge resolves normal mode or Boss mode (`@jarvis`, `@gemini`, `@codex`, `@claude`).
+3. Unified memory reconstructs context (4 layers).
+4. Agent classifies task โ’ selects provider/model โ’ executes agentic loop.
+5. Result is normalized, token usage tracked, and response returned.
+6. Background tasks: fact extraction, summarization, self-reflection.
