+## 3. Agent Class (Core AI Engine)
+
+**File**: `server/src/bot_agents/agent.ts` (1,144 lines)
+
+This is the heart of the system โ€” an **Autonomous AI Agent** with ReAct-style planning.
+
+### Processing Pipeline
+
+1. **Task Classification** (`config/aiConfig.ts`) โ€” classifies into: GENERAL, COMPLEX, CODE, DATA, THINKING, VISION, WEB_BROWSER, SYSTEM
+2. **Provider Routing** โ€” selects AI model per task type + per-bot override + health-aware failover
+3. **Memory Context Build** โ€” 4-layer context from `unifiedMemory.buildContext()`
+4. **ReAct Planning** (for COMPLEX/CODE/DATA/THINKING, messages > 30 chars) โ€” generates execution plan via lightweight model
+5. **Persona + System Instruction** โ€” loads persona config + bot identity + core memory + archival + learnings + goals + plan context
+6. **Agentic Loop** โ€” iterates LLM calls + tool execution until final text response (max turns per task type)
+7. **Reviewer Gate** (optional) โ€” cross-checks response quality before delivery
+8. **Background Enrichment** (async) โ€” archival extraction, core profile extraction, summarization, self-reflection
+
+### Turn Limits per Task Type
+
+| Task Type | Max Turns |
+|-----------|-----------|
+| GENERAL | 10 |
+| SYSTEM | 5 |
+| COMPLEX | 25 |
+| CODE | 20 |
+| DATA | 20 |
+| THINKING | 25 |
+| VISION | 8 |
+| WEB_BROWSER | 15 |
+
+### Failover Chain
+
+Intra-provider (Gemini): `gemini-2.5-flash โ’ gemini-2.5-flash-lite โ’ gemini-2.0-flash โ’ gemini-2.0-flash-lite โ’ gemini-1.5-flash`
+
+Cross-provider: cycles through `Agent.FALLBACK_CHAIN` (openai, openrouter, minimax)
+
+### Safety Mechanisms
+
+- Agent timeout: 120s (`AGENT_TIMEOUT_MS`)
+- Tool timeout: 45s (`TOOL_TIMEOUT_MS`)
+- Tool output truncation: 12,000 chars (`MAX_TOOL_OUTPUT`)
+- Parallel tool max: 5 concurrent (`PARALLEL_TOOL_MAX`)
+- Tool retry: max 2 retries with exponential backoff (800ms base)
+- Circuit breaker per tool (auto-disable after repeated failures)
+- Per-user message queue (prevents concurrent processing for same user)
+- Consecutive error threshold: 3 โ’ forces text response, abandons plan
+
+### Key Dependencies
+
+- `agentTelemetry.ts` โ€” run tracking, circuit breaker, per-user queue
+- `agentPhase2.ts` โ€” reviewer gate, execution plan parsing, retryable error detection
+- `config/aiConfig.ts` โ€” task classification logic
+- `config/configManager.ts` โ€” runtime configuration
+- `ai/personaManager.ts` โ€” persona loading per platform
