+## 16. Smoke Test Checklist
+
+1. Login dashboard โ’ verify protected endpoints return 200
+2. Send LINE and Telegram message โ’ verify bot response
+3. Summon each boss mode โ’ `@jarvis`, `@gemini`, `@codex`, `@claude`
+4. Launch batch from Multi-Agent Center โ’ verify 3 lanes receive work
+5. Confirm per-lane token footer updates
+6. Open Jarvis Terminal โ’ run commands
+7. Check Memory Viewer โ’ verify 4-layer memory data
+8. Verify server console is not flooded with noise
